examples.en: She was given the starring role.
The actress is starring in a daffy new comedy this summer.
DiCaprio became all the rage after starring in the film 'Titanic'.
She is starring in another melodrama.
Any film starring Tom Cruise always packs them in.
...the eagerly anticipated new movie starring our favorite actor turned out to be a big letdown...
'The Freshman' was Brando's first starring role (=the most important part in a film) in ten years.
